---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Thoughts on Linux, cloud infrastructure, DevOps, and lessons from 30+ years in the field.
---
<div class="blog-index">
  <h1>Blog</h1>
  <p class="blog-intro">Thoughts on Linux, cloud infrastructure, DevOps, and lessons from 30+ years in the field.</p>

  {% if collections.blog.length %}
  <ul class="post-list">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <li class="post-item">
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-link">
        <span class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
        <span class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</span>
      </a>
      {% if post.data.description %}
      <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if post.data.tags %}
      <div class="post-tags">
        {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
          {% if tag != "blog" %}
          <a href="/tags/{{ tag }}/" class="tag">{{ tag }}</a>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  {% else %}
  <p>Posts coming soon.</p>
  {% endif %}

  <p class="rss-link"><a href="/feed.xml">RSS Feed</a></p>
</div>
